snippet.title: Mutant Boxing League – Trailer
snippet.description:
Filmic Studios invites you to dive into the thrill of boxing in VR! Battle champion fighters in exotic locales for an unbeatable workout. Face unique opponents, unlock new challenges, and wield special gloves. Join our beta for the ultimate VR boxing experience – exclusively on Meta Quest 2 and 3. Let's play and become the boxing champion you were meant to be!
